showlogin Plugin for DokuWiki

Show login-page if user is not logged in and ACL restricts access to wanted wikipage

All documentation for this plugin can be found at
https://github.com/igittigitt/dokuwiki-plugin-showlogin/zipball/master

If you install this plugin manually, make sure it is installed in
lib/plugins/showlogin/ - if the folder is called different it
will not work!

Please refer to http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugins for additional info
on how to install plugins in DokuWiki.

